These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, punk
City: miami, paris
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Music-Genre         | punk | electronic  |
| City       | paris    | miami    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, aristoff
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, april
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Cigar           | swisher | aristoff      |
| Birthday   | april  | january      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, february
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, gardening
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Birthday          | december    | february   |
| Hobby   | gardening  | fishing   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

