.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, april
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
2 different games are played: whist, billiard
1. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Birthday      | january       | april |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Game   | whist           | billiard   |

