.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country       |
| Nationality         | australian   | japanese |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike     |

