.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, indian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
2 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the british is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the british is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person playing chess is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | indian | british     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Game           | chess          | mah-jongg    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 